# HTTP/gRPC Requests for chat-service
# Port: 50052

### CreateChannel
GRPC localhost:50052/slykat_chat_app.ChatService/CreateChannel
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "string",
  "creator_id": "string"
}

### SendMessage
GRPC localhost:50052/slykat_chat_app.ChatService/SendMessage
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "channel_id": "string",
  "sender_id": "string",
  "content": "string"
}

### GetMessages
GRPC localhost:50052/slykat_chat_app.ChatService/GetMessages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "channel_id": "string",
  "limit": 0,
  "offset": 0
}
